Anyway, glib pseudo-wisdom aside, the short answer to your question is: your AE dots have a slightly longer range than the melee ranges of most mobs. Keep the mobs inside AE song range but just outside melee range.
<br />

<br />
The long answer to your question is... seriously, read the guides. Read the thread &quot;AoE kiting - Front's 0 to 50 in 2 weeks for the poor man.&quot; There is SO MUCH material on AE kiting on this site it's not even funny, you could sit and read it for days, you just need to look for it.</span></td>
